snippet.title: Legend of Krannia - Mage Gameplay (Introducing the monsters)
snippet.description:
Hello Krannians!

Welcome to another Mage build gameplay for Legend of Krannia: Cursed Fate! For this video, we will introduce you to some of the enemies in Volume 1. This video will also show you some strategies for your Mage build. Let us know what you think! 

If you want to see more build, you can subscribe to our channel.
If you have any comments or feedback, don't hesitate to comment bellow or join our discord channel.

Thank you and see you in the next video!

Get your Copy NOW!! Take advantage of the Early Access! 
( Steam Store Page ) -  https://store.steampowered.com/app/1458340/Legend_of_Krannia_Cursed_Fate/
( itch.io Store Page ) - https://aethernum.itch.io/
